1494
01:39:51,320 --> 01:39:53,100
<i>Well, uh...</i>

1495
01:39:53,200 --> 01:39:54,700
<i>I suppose you could say...</i>

1496
01:39:54,800 --> 01:39:58,340
<i>we've been having a few dozen
